title: Independent Inam Bari wins PP-238 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 09 (APP): Independent Candidate, Inam Bari has won the Punjab Assembly election from PP-238 Bahawalnagar-II by securing 54,500 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Syed Nazar Mahmood Shah of Pakistan Muslim League-Nawaz (PML-N) who bagged 49,401 votes.
Overall votersâ€™ turn-out remained 60.09 percent.
